    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally pampered, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and is ready to hit the road with zero worries. If you're looking for a ride that's basically perfect, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
