    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Alpine White. Powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, this unit features a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The double-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced to ensure optimal torsional rigidity. With original paint depth readings and untouched factory suspension geometry, this example retains its stock kinematics and handling precision. The interior features flawless Nappa leather, and the engine bay is free of any fluid seepage or thermal cycling fatigue. A true purist\u2019s specimen with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 47900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
