    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably maintained specimen, representing the absolute pinnacle of its model line. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a level of preservation that is increasingly rare in the current market. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, hand-selected interior materials, speaks to a history of meticulous stewardship. Mechanically beyond reproach and aesthetically unrivaled, this vehicle offers a singular opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire an investment-grade motorcar of the highest caliber.",
      "price": 49500.0,
