    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It's been my absolute pride and joy, and I've kept it in truly pristine condition\u2014it basically still looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! From the sparkling paint to that fresh interior smell, it\u2019s flawless. I\u2019m only selling because I\u2019m looking to downsize, but I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin, you'll fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
