      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of the S54-powered era. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies, with the high-pressure VANOS system fully serviced for optimal cam timing. The chassis is structurally impeccable, featuring a proactively reinforced rear subframe and a pristine suspension geometry. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth and interior trim are in showroom state, free of typical bolster wear or trim degradation. A mechanically superlative, collector-grade example with a comprehensive service history.",
